#~ msgid ""
#~ "For those with a deep interest in the taxonomy of free X terminals, there "
#~ "are two others of this kind: <application>xterm</application>, the "
#~ "original, written even before X itself (a month or two), and "
#~ "<application>xvt</application>, a lightweight <application>xterm</"
#~ "application> clone, on which most other currently available derivatives "
#~ "(notably <application>eterm</application>) are based."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "For dem med en dyb interesse i udviklingen af frie X-terminaler, er der "
#~ "to andre af denne slags: <application>xterm</application>, den "
#~ "oprindelige, skrevet før X selv (en måned eller to), og <application>xvt</"
#~ "application>, en letvægts <application>xterm</application>-klon, på "
#~ "hvilken de fleste andre aktuelt tilgængelige afledte (specielt "
#~ "<application>eterm</application>) er baserede."

